>https://ipsw.me/iPhone15,4</a> ，属于工厂预装（ Preinstalled ），只有代工厂能拿到。这个版本是专为新款手机打造的，经过研发过程长时间测试，发热和续航都很不错，后期升级是给所有型号的手机，不会为某一个型号单独优化。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1716120834, "replies": 71, "id": 1042069}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1700771269", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1700771269", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 62782, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1700771269", "stars": 8966, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 359662, "username": "basncy", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/basncy", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/d933cc2cac223cdf7b8aa0ada634874d?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/d933cc2cac223cdf7b8aa0ada634874d?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/d933cc2cac223cdf7b8aa0ada634874d?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1540884171, "last_modified": 1700908237}, "last_reply_by": "datou", "last_touched": 1716169533, "title": "劝大家不要用微软的邮箱, 会丢信且无提示.", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1042033", "created": 1716107346, "deleted": 0, "content": "它家有 IP 黑名单(关键字: S3140), 直接把某些小厂的邮件丢了, 连垃圾箱都不会进.\r\n现象是, 发件人点击发送后, 然后就没有然后了. 这封信不仅收件人的邮箱(包括垃圾箱)找不到, 连发件人这边有可观的概率没有退信提示(显示已发送).\r\n\r\n好处是垃圾箱清静, 坏处是收件箱也清静, 结果是可用性 80%.\r\n\r\nhttps://answers.microsoft.com/en-us/outlook_com/forum/all/hotmailoutlook-block-list-s3140-blocks-all-new/699f3a56-406e-4804-97e2-cbe23b9bb01c", "content_rendered": "它家有 IP 黑名单(关键字: S3140), 直接把某些小厂的邮件丢了, 连垃圾箱都不会进.<br />现象是, 发件人点击发送后, 然后就没有然后了. 这封信不仅收件人的邮箱(包括垃圾箱)找不到, 连发件人这边有可观的概率没有退信提示(显示已发送).<br /><br />好处是垃圾箱清静, 坏处是收件箱也清静, 结果是可用性 80%.<br /><br /><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://answers.microsoft.com/en-us/outlook_com/forum/all/hotmailoutlook-block-list-s3140-blocks-all-new/699f3a56-406e-4804-97e2-cbe23b9bb01c\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://answers.microsoft.com/en-us/outlook_com/forum/all/hotmailoutlook-block-list-s3140-blocks-all-new/699f3a56-406e-4804-97e2-cbe23b9bb01c</a>", "last_modified": 1716107346, "replies": 66, "id": 1042033}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4a0/42cf/171_large.png?m=1630576706", "name": "invest", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4a0/42cf/171_normal.png?m=1630576706", "title": "投资", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/invest", "topics": 1575, "footer": "", "header": "Can you make money with money?", "title_alternative": "Invest", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4a0/42cf/171_mini.png?m=1630576706", "stars": 2678, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 171, "parent_node_name": "money"}, "member": {"id": 545903, "username": "lalalaXxx", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/lalalaXxx", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ea32/2207/545903_mini.png?m=1621582219", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ea32/2207/545903_normal.png?m=1621582219", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/ea32/2207/545903_large.png?m=1621582219", "created": 1621558874, "last_modified": 1621582219}, "last_reply_by": "LokiSharp", "last_touched": 1716146903, "title": "20W 求一手国内最佳理财", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1041974", "created": 1716088194, "deleted": 0, "content": "## 需求\r\n\t\r\n    刚完婚，手里大概 30W 现金，想做理财；\r\n    \r\n    10W 已经在 PEPE 8500 的时候 合约 x5 入场了;\r\n    \r\n    还有 20W 想做国内稳定理财 只考虑国内，稳定，利益最大化,接受半年内的死期；\r\n    \r\n    求大佬推荐；", "content_rendered": "<h2>需求</h2>\n<pre><code>刚完婚，手里大概 30W 现金，想做理财；\n\n10W 已经在 PEPE 8500 的时候 合约 x5 入场了;\n\n还有 20W 想做国内稳定理财 只考虑国内，稳定，利益最大化,接受半年内的死期；\n\n求大佬推荐；\n</code></pre>\n", "last_modified": 1716092701, "replies": 63, "id": 1041974}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1608969785", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1608969785", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 5855, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785", "stars": 1424, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 676983, "username": "hallostr", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/hallostr", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3f42/923a/676983_mini.png?m=1715067477", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3f42/923a/676983_normal.png?m=1715067477", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3f42/923a/676983_large.png?m=1715067477", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3f42/923a/676983_xlarge.png?m=1715067477", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3f42/923a/676983_xlarge.png?m=1715067477", "created": 1708588734, "last_modified": 1715067477}, "last_reply_by": "frankkly", "last_touched": 1716169549, "title": "大家夏天用凉席吗？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1042004", "created": 1716098800, "deleted": 0, "content": "前几天一个想法，夏天不用电风扇，执行一个星期就放弃了  \r\n原因是空调太闷了，没那么热还是开窗户+风扇舒服，记得买自然风那种  \r\n\r\n小时候家里都用凉席的，就是竹子编的那种；但是生活条件好了，空调可以整晚开，感觉凉席用的好少了（小红书搜的）；代替的有粗布，冰丝席等等..  \r\n但是我感觉效果都不如竹席舒服啊，尤其是快天亮的时候，空调关闭以后温度开始回升；所以又想重新买竹席，大家一般夏天都用啥凉席避暑，有没有推荐的竹席啊", "content_rendered": "<p>前几天一个想法，夏天不用电风扇，执行一个星期就放弃了<br/>\n原因是空调太闷了，没那么热还是开窗户+风扇舒服，记得买自然风那种  </p>\n<p>小时候家里都用凉席的，就是竹子编的那种；但是生活条件好了，空调可以整晚开，感觉凉席用的好少了（小红书搜的）；代替的有粗布，冰丝席等等..<br/>\n但是我感觉效果都不如竹席舒服啊，尤其是快天亮的时候，空调关闭以后温度开始回升；所以又想重新买竹席，大家一般夏天都用啥凉席避暑，有没有推荐的竹席啊</p>\n", "last_modified": 1716115867, "replies": 53, "id": 1042004}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/nava